{"id":604854,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/01/盐邦论坛-盐城一老人开出人尚在还活着证明/","date":"2019-01-28T18:49:57Z","modified":"2019-01-28T18:53:11Z","title":"盐邦论坛 | 盐城一老人开出“人尚在”还活着证明！","content":"<p>文章原标题：再现奇葩，盐城一老人开出“人尚在”还活着证明！<br />\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604855\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/1-8.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"78\" /></p>\n<p>盐城又惊现奇葩证明、证明：＂人尚在、还活着＂！据说这是盐城的一位市民长期在陕西西安某地工作、现在西安工作地为了养老保险的问题非要老人到盐城老家出具这个奇葩证明证明自己还活着！<br />\n国家三令五申禁止这种奇葩证明的存在、也不知西安的什么部门非要这种证明自己还活着的证明、真的是笑话！</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604856\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/2-7.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"776\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/2-7.png 520w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/2-7-193x300.png 193w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604857\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/3-5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/3-5.png 799w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/3-5-300x225.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/3-5-768x577.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604858\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/4-4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/4-4.png 525w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/4-4-225x300.png 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-604859\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/5-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"242\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/5-3.png 469w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/01/5-3-300x145.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-